{"tid":730152,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"哥迪奧拿：「英格蘭能進入八強，最大功勞是我！」","createTime":"2018-07-05T07:24:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T08:02:28.000Z","uid":19889,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"70066d7eeaa4ecb4b44cc4d7688a25ab94272d11","tid":730152,"uid":19889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T07:24:03.000Z","msg":"英格蘭破天荒進入世界盃八強比賽，更破紀錄在互射十二碼之下分勝負，令不少英格蘭球迷狂歡起來。<br />\n<br />\n現任英超冠軍曼城領隊哥迪奧拿接受法國Nineup報獨家訪問時表示，英格蘭在是次世界盃的表現，他的功勞功不可沒。「當我準備接手掌管曼城時，早已知道祖赫特的能力，因此到步第一件事就是把他送走。」<br />\n<br />\n祖赫特總共被外借兩個球季，分別是意甲拖連奴和韋斯咸，兩季的表演都令球迷大跌眼鏡。「祖赫特被外借後能力原形畢露了，憎恨我的球迷應該無話可說了。」祖赫特差勁的表演令自己失去英格蘭第一門將的位置，更落選了英格蘭大軍。<br />\n<br />\n對於英格蘭首度互射十二碼勝利，哥迪奧拿摸摸自己的光頭回應：「英格蘭能進入八強，最大功勞是我，要不是我證明了祖赫特的表現，三獅軍早就在十六強被哥倫比亞中出了。」<br />\n<br />\n最後，記者問到英格蘭會否奪下大力神盃，哥迪奧拿舉起了兩根手指：「我執教西甲時，西班牙奪得了世界盃冠軍；我執教德甲時，德國奪得了世界盃冠軍；現在我執教英超了，你說呢？」<br />\n<br />\n哥迪奧拿離開訪問時，回頭說笑：「看來中超球會出一億周薪找我執教，我都要抬高價錢了。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/gZeYa-6lYVM/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FgZeYa-6lYVM%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=f15e36c3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9cb0a96b2763e25d78ec0602167d125ecc59721b","tid":730152,"uid":171107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T07:27:23.000Z","msg":"哥迪奧拿舉起了兩根手指：「我執教西甲時，西班牙奪得了世界盃冠軍；我執教德甲時，德國奪得了世界盃冠軍；現在我執教英超了，你說呢？」<br />\n<br />\n有啲道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69b47dfa74795a271b7e081513eb88748f9ad2db","tid":730152,"uid":21716,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T07:30:30.000Z","msg":"哥狗中文幾好喎，中出都識用！"},{"pid":"ac812a41a97e38012f8e9e3dce9acfc35664c12e","tid":730152,"uid":66839,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T07:31:43.000Z","msg":"9up報"},{"pid":"2a8710450bbcf088e09bed90c547a3cf86577d8e","tid":730152,"uid":12510,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T07:36:47.000Z","msg":"睇完最後個句<br />\n<br />\n呢篇應該係潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a9bcdaf549c316374a6d03ad885373f1a0cc26e","tid":730152,"uid":66825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T07:37:34.000Z","msg":"搵佢黎教香港試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢好似幾憎祖赫特<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbe50eb4d1deea8ffa3b0033dfcdc0e6107543c6","tid":730152,"uid":19889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a9bcdaf549c316374a6d03ad885373f1a0cc26e","tid":730152,"uid":66825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T07:37:34.000Z","msg":"搵佢黎教香港試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢好似幾憎祖赫特<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T07:47:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.kfs.io/artist/global/11261,0v2/fit/300x300.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.kfs.io%2Fartist%2Fglobal%2F11261%2C0v2%2Ffit%2F300x300.jpg&h=df58af2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n祖赫特"},{"pid":"741e000bb01dcc2feec4ea8e0a2e7601d5e394d2","tid":730152,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac812a41a97e38012f8e9e3dce9acfc35664c12e","tid":730152,"uid":66839,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T07:31:43.000Z","msg":"9up報"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T08:02:28.000Z","msg":"我都以為係仲達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}